parameters: Clea: Why are you in such a hurry, Neuro-san?

Tailor Neuro: There's a tailor shop in Beach Lepton where I
have some deliveries to make. The deadline is approaching,
so I need to hurry back.

Tailor Neuro: That's why I'm grateful! Besides, if I can
witness a battle, it might inspire me!

Tailor Neuro: That's right, it's necessary for the design! I
need explosive inspiration!

Sailor: There's a ship silhouette ahead! It's likely the
Pirate Gang of Pirata!

Captain Agwa: They're coming towards us at an incredible
speed... It's going to be a battle!
Clea: Neuro-san, please take shelter inside the ship.

Tailor Neuro: Didn't I just say it earlier? I'm staying
behind for inspiration!
Clea: It's dangerous, so please go inside--
Clea: Why are you in such a hurry, Nora?

Tailor Nora: I have a tailor shop in Beach Lepton, and I
need to hurry back because the deadline for delivering the
goods is approaching.

Tailor Nora: That's why I'm grateful! Besides, if I can
witness a battle, it might inspire me!

Tailor Nora: That's right, it's necessary for the design! I
need an explosive inspiration!

Sailor: There's a ship silhouette ahead! It's likely the
Pirate Gang of Pirata!

Captain Agua: They're coming towards us at an incredible
speed... It's going to be a battle!
Clea: Nora, please take shelter inside the ship.

Tailor Nora: Didn't I just say it? I'm staying behind for
the sake of inspiration!
Clea: It's dangerous, so please go inside--

Captain Agua: They crashed into our ship! Check the
condition of the ship right away, hurry, it might sink!

Clea: They've arrived...! I will definitely protect this
ship until the end.
Pirate Gang Crew Member: H-Help us! The ship is sinking!
Thief Nora: Hey, something seems strange...?

Priestess Sophia: Hmm, could it be a rift among our allies?
Ugh... the rocking of the ship after all...

Mage Relm: I-I understand the reason... These people...
They've brought something unbelievable, haven't they?

Clea: It seems like the only way to reach Beach Lepton is to
defeat this monster...
Clea: Are there still crew members on board?

Pirate Gang Crew Member: Ah, the captain is still on the
ship...
Clea: Let's help them. It's also our job to capture you.
Pirate Gang Crew Member: Ah... please... help us...!

Tailor Neuro: Heroic feats of defeating monsters! A
compassionate heart that helps even enemies... This is it,
this is it!

Tailor Neuro: I have a feeling that a masterpiece is about
to be born!
